title: 50 Rolls, 2 1/4”x 50’ Golden Wind Thermal Paper Till Receipt Roll for PDQ Credit Card Machine, POS, EPOS, 55gsm Premium Quality 57 * 40mm (Roll Diameter)
features: DIMENSION: The paper roll is 2.25" wide 50 feet long (GUARANTEED), also labeled as 57*40mm(Roll diameter).
PACKAGE: 50 rolls/box, also shrink wrapped to protect from the moisture and being damaged in transportation.
STORAGE: To ensure the best quality of print, please store thermal receipt in a dry, normal temperature environment (lower than 60 °C).
CRISP PRINT： The printing is crisp and bold, no toner or ink needed, easy to sign, at least 3 years image life.
HIGH COMPATIBILITY Our Thermal Paper Receipt Roll fits most of common square credit card terminals in market.
description: Product Description Smooth and Thick With over 30 years paper industry experience, we always try to provide premium quality receipt rolls well-balanced in smoothness and thickness (55gsm), which enables you to print great quality image in a fast speed. CRISP AND BOLD The premium quality receipt will bring you a crips and bold print, which is durable, and easy to sign. The red stripe of running out mark will remind you to change a new roll to avoid the impact to business caused by receipt running out. We try every efforts to manage the cost down in each step, we use small core for our receipt rolls to save overall size, we provide the paper length as we described, you may check and compare with other brands you used before WIDE APPLICATION GOLDEN WIND thermal receipt is widely used by many business, such as cafe, hotel, restaurant, medical, bank and logistic, our roll fits most of cash register, point of sales and credit card terminals in market. We put extra care in pack and deliver, 10 rolls/poly bag shrink wrapped, 50 rolls packed in carton box to ensure the rolls are delivered in good condition to our customers.
